就是这样","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"fes3-KO-part1-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薰","body":"这真让人担心。\n希望你至少今晚能做个好梦……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"serious01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"fes3-KO-part1-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"育美","body":"育美听说过做快乐的梦的方法哦！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"fes3-KO-part1-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"美咲","body":"真的吗？现在我什么都愿意试试，告诉我吧","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"fes3-KO-part1-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"育美","body":"睡觉前看一看让人开心的图画或是书！\n那样的话，内容就会出现在梦里哦！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId"